				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Hu%E1%BB%87/Ch%E1%BB%A9c-c%E1%BA%A9m-h%E1%BB%93i-v%C4%83n/poem-nF5ajtrF4j4zC0ZRfPADLA">Chức cẩm hồi văn - 織錦回文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Hu%E1%BB%87/author-KOtVUs_kcoFrZTmRo_4QbA">Tô Huệ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/%C4%90%C4%83ng-H%E1%BB%97-s%C6%A1n-h%E1%BB%AFu-c%E1%BA%A3m/poem-uduF2gJdukyw8FuHydwPgw">Đăng Hỗ sơn hữu cảm - 登岵山有感</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/%C4%90%E1%BB%99c-b%E1%BA%A5t-ki%E1%BA%BFn/poem-B9lWygzL4oeyMwyR9H5LBQ">Độc bất kiến - 獨不見</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/H%C3%AD-t%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%C6%B0-k%C3%BD/poem-jwaWWRGPiRiwsd25KMg5VA">Hí tặng Trương thư ký - 戲贈張書記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Tri%E1%BB%87t/L%C3%BD-phu-nh%C3%A2n-ph%C3%BA/poem-F4vTwWaB-LfUWUH3PUmhdg">Lý phu nhân phú - 李夫人賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Tri%E1%BB%87t/author-gLGd-Bchdqe6FBWqpEd9Qw">Lưu Triệt</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/M%E1%BA%A1nh-%C4%91%C3%B4ng/poem-BEsWkcsvl9u0_2PuMhYLDQ">Mạnh đông - 孟冬</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c/T%E1%BA%A1-t%C3%A2n-%C3%A2n-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-A-cg5LOiDU8UnqCmBeVIBA">Tạ tân ân kỳ 2 - 謝新恩其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c/author-x2jHtUhu4KZY4kl0A-lAIw">Lý Dục</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/Thi%E1%BB%87p-giang-th%C3%A1i-ph%C3%B9-dung/poem-Ipzs0OEPM1qTtzEygLXySg">Thiệp giang thái phù dung - 涉江採芙蓉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/Ti%E1%BA%BFn-%C4%91%E1%BB%83-Ph%C3%BA-Xu%C3%A2n-ki%E1%BB%81u-ti%E1%BB%83u-kh%E1%BA%BF-th%C6%B0-ho%C3%A0i-nh%E1%BB%8B-t%C3%A1c-k%E1%BB%B3-2-H%E1%BB%B1u-th%E1%BA%A5t-ng%C3%B4n-c%E1%BB%95-phong-th%E1%BA%ADp-th%E1%BA%A5t-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-XuZKtYJKOzb4mYIO4yEZ8Q">Tiến để Phú Xuân kiều tiểu khế, thư hoài nhị tác kỳ 2 - Hựu thất ngôn cổ phong thập thất vận - 進抵富春橋小憩，書懷二作其二－又七言古風十七韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/author-geNjG6kbAxWPLaqdF181sQ">Phan Huy Ích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-k%C3%BD-nh%C3%A0n-tam-t%C3%A1c-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-ctcfUqGa8ILF__ofd4yBBg">Xuân nhật ký nhàn tam tác kỳ 2 - 春日記閒三作其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/author-geNjG6kbAxWPLaqdF181sQ">Phan Huy Ích</a>)<br></div>	</div>
